Package cz.cuni.mff.dataset_products

package cz.cuni.mff.dataset_products
This package contains classes that represent the dataset products. It defines classes for products extracted from Zalando (see ZalandoProduct) and Zoot (see ZootProduct) websites. It also handles the deserialization of products from JSON files into these classes.
